WELCOM TO THE NUMBERS GAME
the game and the rules are very simple.
=> first a number of 4 digits is being generated and the 4 digits are not duplicated numbers.
=> you should try to know the number by guessing.
=> you should write a number of 4 digits and the 4 digits should not be duplicated.
=> you should write numbers until you guess the number that generatd by the system.
=> you should try to know it by fewer tries.
=> the rule is that your number will be compared with the generated number and give you the results as the following
=> the results of the comparasing will be like 'x' and 'o' or '----' .
=> x: means that there is one of your numbers is there in the generated number and the number in the same location.
=> o: means that there is one of your numbers is there in the generated number and the number is in different location.
=> ----: means that there is not any of your numbers are in the generated number.
=> for example: if your number was '1234' and the generated number was '1542' you will get 'oox'
that means there are three digits of your number are exist in the generated number
and 1 digit in the same place as in the generated number and the other two are in differet places.
=> so you will keep trying until you will get 'xxxx' then that means that you know the number
SO DO YOU WANT TO PLAY THIS GAME ?
